    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Atlanta Journal,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Atlanta, Georgia.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Dear Sir:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "On July 25, 1948, I mailed a letter enclosing .35 cents in coin and an airmail self-addressed envelop to your circulation department, asking for tear sheets of the Atlanta Journal containing the stories on a \"strange\" or \"mysterious\" aircraft seen near Montgomery, Alabama, July 24, 1948, by two pilots, Capt C. S. Chiles and John B. Whitted, of the Eastern Air Lines.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "These have not arrived. I asked for two copies each of the stories.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Enclosed is an additional .35 cents, and another stamped self-ad-dressed envelop. Will you kindly see that your circulation department com-plies with this simple request?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "I assure you that my interest in the above stories is prompted by interest in the defense of our country, and you are hereby given my fullest permission to turn this letter requesting the copies of the stories over to the FBI, should you wish.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Thanking you very kindly, I am,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Sincerely,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
